‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ requirements.txt      # Dependencies
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ README.md             # Project documentation
```

### Dependencies

Dependencies are managed via `setup.py` and `requirements.txt`.

To reinstall or update:

```bash
pip install -e .
```

